 Syntax:
 `FROM`         Base image            
 `WORKDIR`     Set working directory 
 `COPY`        Copy files            
 `ADD`         Copy + extract        
 `RUN`         Execute commands      
 `EXPOSE`      Document port         
 `ENV`         Environment variables 
 `CMD`         Default command       
 `ENTRYPOINT`  Main command          
 `LABEL`       Metadata              |
